    "MechanismMain contributionDL[217]SLDesign a novel neural network for parameter estimation.DL[218]SLPropose a DL-based channel estimation algorithm for ISAC in vehicular systems.Parameter estimationDL, GAI [219]SLA transformer-based joint data detection and parameter estimation algorithm is proposed.DL, VAEs [220]SLA DNN for parameter estimation of extended target is developed.DL[74]USLPropose a DNN for joint transmitted waveform and phase-shift optimization.DRL[221]RLA model-free DRL algorithm is proposed for dynamic power and sub-carrier allocation.Waveform designDRL[222]RLPropose a model-based DRL algorithm for interference management within ISAC networks.DL[223]USLDesign a DNN for joint transmit waveform and receive beamforming optimization.DRL[224]RLPropose a DRL-based waveform design scheme for automatous vehicles.DL[75]USLDesign a DNN with novel loss function for predictive beamforming.DL[225]SLPropose a DL-based angle estimation algorithm for vehicular networks.Predictive beamformingDL DL[226] [227]USL USLA novel predictive beamforming protocol with low overhead is developed.",
